{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日日間炎熱，稍後有幾陣驟雨。隨後一兩日天氣不穩定，驟雨增多及有雷暴。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月26日(日)</cell>\n        <cell>4月27日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>4月28日(二)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南至東南風3至4級，高地間中5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n        <cell>65-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n        <cell>高</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。稍後有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，間中有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月29日(三)</cell>\n        <cell>4月30日(四)</cell>\n        <cell>5月1日(五)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>21度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>南至西南風3至4級，漸轉東北風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4至5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4至5級，離岸間中6級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n        <cell>65-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>高</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>多雲，間中有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。早上有一兩陣驟雨，天氣稍涼。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。日間部分時間天色明朗。有一兩陣微雨。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T23:07:39.386739+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":474,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}